GCMC CO2 in IRMOF

use gaspressure
finish

temperature 208.0 # temp in K

ewald prec 1e-6

steps         100000
equilibration 10000
print         1000
stack         1000
sample coordinates 1000

# GCMC optimisation
acceptmolmoveupdate 200
acceptmolmoveratio 0.5
acceptmolrotupdate 200
acceptmolrotratio  0.5


# GCMC moves
move molecule    1 25
CO2
move rotatemol   1 25
CO2
move gcinsertmol 1 50 1.0  # atom types, freq, overlap distance
CO2 {pressure}
start
